author: julianfoad
msg: Remove magic string length constants and a duplicative function.
(writebuf_write_short_string): Delete. This function was a wrapper around
writebuf_write that essentially repeated the same optimization.
(...everywhere else...): Use writebuf_write_literal instead of passing a
magic string length constant to writebuf_write_short_string.
